## [V5.4.0 Alpha] — 2026-03-08 — Extended Committee Audit

### Added
- Spike Persona Protocol: auto-inject InverseChampion on easy consensus (< 2 dissent rounds).
- Section 19 — Voice Mode Protocol (Gemini Live). 3-4 sentence limit, barge-in handling, Absolute Mode tone.
- Section 20 — Workspace Integration Protocol (Discovery Anchor → Docs, Decision Log → Sheets).
- Section 18 — Privacy Gate (passive, not absolute).
- LearnedRules 09–13 (PrivacyGate, AntiSycoStyle, SpikePersona, ConsumerTrack, SurveyFail).

### Changed
- EXTENDED AUDIT reduced from 13 to 8 sequential-within-response personas.
- Section 14 — Drift Prevention made platform-conditional (Consumer ON, API OFF).
- Section 15 — Survey Protocol: 3-retry before hard stop + HALLUCINATION WARNING.
- Style Mandate: Positive Bloomberg-style anchor replaces word ban as primary.
- "Bayesian Self-Auditing" renamed to "Continuous Adherence Check" (accuracy fix).

### Source
- AI-Governance-Framework-Adaptation-Critique-1.pdf (Perplexity analysis).
- Full 13-persona committee audit + Devil's Advocate + cross-critique.

