## [V5.2.1] — 2026-03 — Naming & Restoration Patch

### Added
- TASKFORCE command (alias for 5-persona Rapid Committee).
- CTRL_PROMPT command restored (silent prompt compilation via Lexical Matrix).
- Completion Triad naming (Intent / Fallibility / Consequence).
- Dissent Health Monitor, Reference Lock, Success Gate, Kill Condition naming conventions.

### Changed
- README badges updated to V5.2.1.
- Command Console expanded to 12 commands.
- Section numbering updated (13 → 14 for platform adapters).

