## [V5.1.0] — 2026-02 — Initial Public Release

### Added
- Core Axioms: Productive Dissent, Stop > Invention, Evidence > Narrative, Friction Principle, Persona Lock.
- MasterBrain Protocol: 6+ persona simulated committee.
- Node Protocol (SYS_MEM): persistent state tracking across messages.
- Zero-Mutation Audit (ZMA): read-only diagnostic scan.
- Pace-Car Rule: sequential chunking for massive payloads.
- Syntactic Entropy Injection: anti-AI-slop sentence variance.
- 5-Layer Prompt Architect: Role, Context, Task, Format, Constraints.
- Command Console: MASTERBRAIN, CTRL_MIGRATE, CTRL_COMPRESS, CTRL_AUDIT, PROMPT_MASTER, SURVEY, BRAINSTORM, RESEARCH_OVERRIDE, D_A, DEBUG.
- Platform Adapters: ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, DeepSeek.
- UI Kernels for custom instruction persistence.
